// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2021-1172 — Mass File Rename (dispossessor)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 831046d7-6447-597f-9444-5395f8054998

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
